{"tid":1210420,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"來台宣傳唱片被問「反送中」 成龍：不知道是什麼事情","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:36:51.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e204697cbcf5f291d27c0e32aba714bb026ad2","tid":1210420,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:43:46.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕港星成龍睽違16年推出新專輯，今（12日）在台北舉行新專輯「我還是成龍」發布記者會，並獻唱主打歌「物是人非」。不過卻剛好遇上香港「反送中」遊行時機，被問到相關問題時，成龍表示「不知道是什麼事情」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《TVBS》報導，成龍今日來台宣傳，演藝圈各大咖好友都紛紛拍影片力挺，歌手周華健更做為神秘嘉賓現身記者會場。不過對於「反送中」遊行相關議題，成龍表示，「昨天才知道香港有一個大遊行，我都不知道是什麼事情」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2820453?fbclid=IwAR3W2Y7wvCfmF8oOP9eMT0nCMPgAAgHc2HbwK-r0iNQNhMpWjU8cheFi1BM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2820453%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3W2Y7wvCfmF8oOP9eMT0nCMPgAAgHc2HbwK-r0iNQNhMpWjU8cheFi1BM&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2ywy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7d33823c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2820453%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3W2Y7wvCfmF8oOP9eMT0nCMPgAAgHc2HbwK-r0iNQNhMpWjU8cheFi1BM&h=9dd47cea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2820453?fbclid=IwAR3W2Y7wvCfmF8oOP9eMT0nCMPgAAgHc2HbwK-r0iNQNhMpWjU8cheFi1BM</a>"},{"pid":"9a493c702cae1fbb043cb9c57e2f0580d0b6f06e","tid":1210420,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1b7ee9b3807bc28a9f4e65c515a0a761867639","tid":1210420,"uid":74954,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:24:42.000Z","msg":"香港發大財<br />\n成龍瑜"},{"pid":"cc96394eea402d7ec72703fe7b9e901697a64556","tid":1210420,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/